00:28:40.700 --> 00:28:45.110
Now, can you describe what
were the most surprising things

00:28:45.110 --> 00:28:48.720
that you learned about in the final
days of Nixon's White House time?

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:51.110
&gt;&gt; Bob Woodward: This
was about his last year,

00:28:51.110 --> 00:28:57.270
while he was under investigation,
and leading to the resignation.

00:28:57.270 --> 00:29:01.910
It, it showed how much it
was a lawyering operation.

00:29:01.910 --> 00:29:04.730
