control, just he was shattered,

00:29:45.500 --> 00:29:53.340
and it was very sad and, you
know, what we often forget

00:29:53.340 --> 00:29:59.140
in reporting is the emotional
impact of these political events,

00:29:59.140 --> 00:30:03.240
and that was kind of
the culmination.

00:30:03.240 --> 00:30:05.100
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: So
