00:31:34.780 --> 00:31:37.970
and it seemed like it was a painful
experience, because everybody

00:31:37.970 --> 00:31:40.200
who kind of knew him then said
your book was not accurate.

00:31:40.200 --> 00:31:42.720
And, can you describe
what that was about?

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:45.850
&gt;&gt; Bob Woodward: Actually they
never said it was not accurate.

00:31:45.850 --> 00:31:51.290
