00:33:42.770 --> 00:33:48.150
that it's the most severe
critics say it was accurate.

00:33:48.150 --> 00:33:54.870
And, you know, it, it's,
it's not a pretty story

00:33:54.870 --> 00:33:59.230
when you say the Supreme Court,
