00:33:59.230 --> 00:34:05.060 position:56%
or interprets the law, that personal
animus and some of the things

00:34:05.060 --> 00:34:08.540
that drive most human
beings one way or another,

00:34:08.540 --> 00:34:10.490
plays a role, and it does.

00:34:10.490 --> 00:34:13.170
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: So,
another book you wrote dealt

00:34:13.170 --> 00:34:17.390
