00:35:36.050 --> 00:35:37.350
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: Let's
talk about President Bush.

00:35:37.350 --> 00:35:39.890
You wrote a book about the
war that we did in Kuwait,

00:35:39.890 --> 00:35:42.870
and that was "The Commanders."

00:35:42.870 --> 00:35:47.640
And in that war, what, who do you
think the hero was that really came

00:35:47.640 --> 00:35:49.950
up with the strategy that
won that war in Kuwait?

00:35:49.950 --> 00:35:53.460
Was it Colin Powell, was it
Schwarzkopf, was it President Bush?

00:35:53.460 --> 00:35:56.740
