00:36:04.150 --> 00:36:11.260
but the genius of the war was, it
was quick, lasted about 40 days,

00:36:11.260 --> 00:36:16.260
minimal US casualties, and
it accomplished the mission

00:36:16.260 --> 00:36:23.900 position:56%
of getting Saddam's Iraqi Republican
Guard and forces out of Kuwait,

00:36:23.900 --> 00:36:27.880
and sending them, and
