hero in the end, was President Bush,

00:36:35.960 --> 00:36:40.300
who put it all together, used
diplomacy, went to Congress

00:36:40.300 --> 00:36:44.690
to get authority, but also listened
to Colin Powell, who was chairman

00:36:44.690 --> 00:36:50.590
of the Joint Chief, saying, we
need 500,000 troops to do this.

00:36:50.590 --> 00:36:51.890
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:
So, when you write books

00:36:51.890 --> 00:36:54.000
