00:37:51.120 --> 00:37:53.870
for a daily publication,
let's say the Washington Post,

00:37:53.870 --> 00:37:56.360
somebody might be less
inclined to talk to you,

00:37:56.360 --> 00:37:59.410
because whatever they say might
be in the newspapers the next day,

00:37:59.410 --> 00:38:01.650
