00:38:33.170 --> 00:38:34.470
that they're talking to me,"

00:38:34.470 --> 00:38:36.770
or do you never tell
anybody who you've talked to?

00:38:36.770 --> 00:38:39.020
&gt;&gt; Bob Woodward: It depends,
