00:44:11.180 --> 00:44:12.480
&gt;&gt; Bob Woodward: Yes.

00:44:12.480 --> 00:44:14.420 position:56%
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: And what was
your impression of President Carter?

00:44:14.420 --> 00:44:16.300
&gt;&gt; Bob Woodward: Well,
the first interview

00:44:16.300 --> 00:44:18.860
with him was his first
month in office,

00:44:18.860 --> 00:44:22.030
