00:44:22.030 --> 00:44:24.560
of Jordan had been
on the CIA payroll.

00:44:24.560 --> 00:44:27.210
And we called the White House,

00:44:27.210 --> 00:44:32.940
and I remember Jody Powell
was the Press Secretary.

00:44:32.940 --> 00:44:36.610
I hadn't covered the
campaign, and I said,

00:44:36.610 --> 00:44:41.220
there's a secret operation
of paying King Hussein.

00:44:41.220 --> 00:44:46.600
The CIA does it, and the
operation is called "No Beef."

00:44:46.600 --> 00:44:53.070
And I remember Jody
Powell going, "No shit!"

00:44:53.070 --> 00:44:57.020
We didn't deal with stuff like
that in Georgia, and then he said,

00:44:57.020 --> 00:45:01.510
"You and Bradley come see Carter
tomorrow morning at 9 o'clock,"

00:45:01.510 --> 00:45:05.600
and Carter, off the
record, confirmed it, and,

00:45:05.600 --> 00:45:10.330
but Ben asked him, will
it harm national security

00:45:10.330 --> 00:45:11.630
if we publish this?

00:45:11.630 --> 00:45:13.200
And Carter said no.

00:45:13.200 --> 00:45:17.560
And of course Brzezinski, who
wasn't invited to the meeting,

00:45:17.560 --> 00:45:25.510
went nuts afterwards, and, and
we published it, and Carter went

00:45:25.510 --> 00:45:29.490
up to the hill and and said some
things that were not factual,

00:45:29.490 --> 00:45:37.720
and I was distressed that again,
after all of Nixon's saying things

00:45:37.720 --> 00:45:40.940
that were not true, I was
distressed that Carter kind

00:45:40.940 --> 00:45:43.160
of couldn't face up
to what happened.

00:45:43.160 --> 00:45:45.050
