almost a gravitational force.

00:46:39.150 --> 00:46:44.360
I've never known it, I
mean, he doesn't blink.

00:46:44.360 --> 00:46:48.190
Now, you blink all the time.

00:46:48.190 --> 00:46:49.880
I blink all the time.

00:46:49.880 --> 00:46:53.380
Well, I think, ever since he
