00:46:53.380 --> 00:46:58.960
to be President, and realized,
contribute every organ in the body

00:46:58.960 --> 00:47:03.040
to the task [laughter]
including your eyes.

00:47:03.040 --> 00:47:04.340
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: Alright.

00:47:04.340 --> 00:47:06.800
Bob Woodward: And so, it
