00:47:29.440 --> 00:47:31.630
are [laughter].

00:47:31.630 --> 00:47:34.800
And I left the interview
thinking, this, you know,

00:47:34.800 --> 00:47:38.420
what a great interview, such
insight, I can use all this,

00:47:38.420 --> 00:47:43.840
and then I read, had a transcript
