00:49:03.070 --> 00:49:06.600
telling Bush it was a slam
dunk that there were weapons

00:49:06.600 --> 00:49:13.280
of mass destruction in Iraq,
the CIA made a terrible mistake,

00:49:13.280 --> 00:49:15.340
but I don't think it was a lie.

00:49:15.340 --> 00:49:20.600
I think it was a tragedy, and
if you go through all the steps,

00:49:20.600 --> 00:49:24.140
you kind of come up, gee, you know,

00:49:24.140 --> 00:49:28.960
he should've realized it was
not necessary to go to war,

00:49:28.960 --> 00:49:33.290 position:56%
but there was a momentum and he, you
