00:49:33.290 --> 00:49:36.100 position:56%
like Joe Biden, and Hillary Clinton,

00:49:36.100 --> 00:49:38.940
who voted to give them the
authority to go to war.

00:49:38.940 --> 00:49:40.740
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: So, have
