be seen as being, doing a good job

00:51:22.010 --> 00:51:24.450
as President of the United
States, and bringing,

00:51:24.450 --> 00:51:25.750
making sure there's no...

00:51:25.750 --> 00:51:28.610
&gt;&gt; Bob Woodward: I mean, the one,
